 href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/shs-international-excellence-scholarship\/#Eligibility_Criteria\" title=\"Eligibility Criteria\">Eligibility Criteria<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/shs-international-excellence-scholarship\/#Application_ProcedureSHS_International_Excellence_Scholarship\" title=\"Application Procedure|SHS International Excellence Scholarship\">Application Procedure|SHS International Excellence Scholarship<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 80px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #003366;\">\u00a0SHS International Excellence Scholarship is open for all international students who wish to apply the scholarship is for undergraduate students the eligibility criteria are given below:<\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80019482\">Scholarship Description:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80019483\">Deadline<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80019484\">Degree Level:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80019485\">Subjects Available<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80019486\">Scholarship Profits<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80019487\"><strong>Scholarship Benefits<\/strong><strong>:<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80019488\">Eligibility Nationalities<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80019489\">Eligibility Criteria<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80019490\">Application Procedure<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"scholarship-description\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Scholarship_Description\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80019482\"><\/a>Scholarship Description:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The SHS International Excellence Scholarship at City of London, UK is open for domestic students, international students. the scholarship allows Masters level program (s) in the field of all subjects except:<\/p>\n<p>MSc Speech and Language Therapy MSc Adult and Mental Health Nursing taught at the City University of London.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"deadlineshs-international-excellence-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"DeadlineSHS_International_Excellence_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80019483\"><\/a>Deadline|SHS International Excellence Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The scholarship dead of the scholarship is 06 December 2024.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"degree-level\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Degree_Level\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80019484\"><\/a>Degree Level:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The International Excellence Scholarship is available to undertake Masters Level.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"subjects-available\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Subjects_Available\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80019485\"><\/a>Subjects Available<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>All subjects are available to study under this scholarship.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"scholarship-profitsshs-international-excellence-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Scholarship_ProfitsSHS_International_Excellence_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80019486\"><\/a>Scholarship Profits|SHS International Excellence Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The City University of London offers<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80019487\"><\/a>Scholarship Benefits<strong>:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>The City University of London offers \u00a31,000 to \u00a35,000 to outstanding international students applying for a place on selected post-registration MSc programs in the School of Health Sciences.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"eligibility-nationalities\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Eligibility_Nationalities\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80019488\"><\/a>Eligibility Nationalities<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Is open for all nationals.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"eligibility-criteria\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Eligibility_Criteria\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80019489\"><\/a>Eligibility Criteria<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>All applicants have an offer of a full-time place and are studying for the MSc on one of SHS\u2019s postgraduate programs.<\/li>\n<li>Candidates for the PG Cert or PG Diploma will not be eligible.<\/li>\n<li>In addition, note that the following two MSc programs are not eligible for this scholarship:<\/li>\n<li>MSc Speech and Language Therapy<\/li>\n<li>MSC Adult and Mental Health Nursing.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-procedureshs-international-excellence-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_ProcedureSHS_International_Excellence_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80019490\"><\/a>Application Procedure|SHS International Excellence Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To apply, please complete the official scholarships form, including a statement of no more than 500 words. This statement will be in addition to the personal state used for the program application and should focus on why you believe you should be awarded this scholarship.<\/p>\n<p>Also within your statement, you could include references to projects or initiatives that you have undertaken in which you have exceeded or work that you have done that have improved practice or how this scholarship could help you advance practice in your chosen area.<\/p>\n<p>To Apply click <a href=\"https:\/\/www.scholarshipsads.com\/shs-international-excellence-scholarship-at-city-university-of-london-uk\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>See Also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<a title=\"Apply Now | Red Deer College Programs 2024\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/red-deer-college-programs\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Apply Now | Red Deer College Programs 2024 <\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"SHS International Excellence Scholarship &#8211; Deadline, Degree level, subjects available, Scholarship benefits, Eligibility Nationalities, Eligibility Criteria, Application Procedure.&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1395,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[829],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1393"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1393"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1393\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1393"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1393"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1393"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}